{"tid":1779711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特赦又點可以包性罪行","createTime":"2019-12-12T00:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T04:11:23.000Z","uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9e78b5e81fb7bb5da031d3b21a5a614a453ae0","tid":1779711,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"性罪行同其他警暴有顯住唔同嘅差別<br />\n更何況無罪行聲明喺警務處都有齋講性罪行嘅版本<br />\n證明社會對呢類罪行有更高要求<br />\n而且容易由其他罪行分辨出黎<br />\n<br />\n非禮、強姦呢啲行為<br />\n絕對同示威活動本身冇關啦<br />\n<br />\n如果要一刀切特赦<br />\n性罪行係唔需要包括在內<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好俾淫警帶到風向"},{"pid":"5354ecc261df2c1b71b04a3448b1ec1fa90ffed9","tid":1779711,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:03:50.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n/////////////////////////<br />\nsorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n手足無證據都坐咗半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話手足唔係condom<br />\n幫推大家關注啦"},{"pid":"bc12e65198b20c6c563e9abd8c5819d93ff52116","tid":1779711,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1779556/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1779556/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係淫警話要特赦性罪行<br />\n而係民主黨何俊仁話要特赦黑警強姦犯"},{"pid":"f3afb27b7259d1db63036d3d8e0dc1438d80e58a","tid":1779711,"uid":330823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定不可特赦,死的年青人不可白死</span></span>"}]}